HEADWORD: Desitive
<hw>Des"i*tive</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Logic)</fld> <def>A proposition
relating to or expressing an end or conclusion.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>I. Watts.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
